      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/edf47de8-79ed-11e4-bb7c-5254006e85c2).  Ran 16 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
